span>善听者，终能找到道路。</span></p>\n      <ul class=\"z05-meta\" aria-label=\"Z05 AuAg highlights\">\n        <li>TwinCore dual voice</li><li>AuAg launch finish</li><li>10mm PET dynamic woofer</li><li>3.5 / 4.4 / Type-C ready</li>\n      </ul>\n      <div class=\"z05-actions\"><a class=\"z05-btn\" href=\"/cart/add?id={{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}&quantity=1\">Buy Z05 AuAg</a><a class=\"z05-btn secondary\" href=\"#z05-twincore\">Hear the TwinCore story</a></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"z05-hero-media\">\n      <img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-luxury-portrait-hero.png' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg Launch Edition in a minimalist gold and silver luxury studio setting\">\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <div class=\"z05-stat-strip\"><div class=\"z05-wrap z05-stats\"><div class=\"z05-stat\"><b>TwinCore</b><span>Blue for weight and flow. Red for openness and focus. Two voicings built for real listening moods.</span></div><div class=\"z05-stat\"><b>Dynamic Bass</b><span>A PET diaphragm 10mm woofer gives kick drums, bass guitars, and synth lines physical shape.</span></div><div class=\"z05-stat\"><b>Hybrid Detail</b><span>Balanced armatures bring vocal presence, separation, and upper harmonic air around the dynamic low end.</span></div><div class=\"z05-stat\"><b>AuAg</b><span>Forged-carbon faceplates carry the Au/Ag identity; the 3D-printed shells are hand-laced and finished pair by pair.</span></div></div></div>\n</div>",
