            "settings": {
                "section_visibility": "always",
                "custom_liquid": "<div id=\"z05-engineering\" class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z05-section dark z05-engineering-section\"><div class=\"z05-wrap\"><div class=\"z05-engineering-head\"><div><p class=\"z05-kicker\">Craft & Sound</p><h2>Faceplate craft, shell precision, hybrid control</h2></div><div class=\"z05-engineering-copy\"><p>Z05 AuAg is built as a universal monitor first: compact fit, repeatable seal, and a driver platform that stays useful across albums, sources, and listening moods.</p><p>The forged-carbon treatment belongs to the faceplates. The body is a 3D-printed shell, then finished with artisanal hand-laced gold and silver foil work. Each pair takes hours to dress, align, and finish before it becomes the AuAg launch edition.</p></div></div><div class=\"z05-craft-strip\" aria-label=\"Z05 AuAg craft notes\"><article><span>Faceplate</span><b>Forged carbon with Au/Ag foil</b></article><article><span>Shell body</span><b>3D-printed universal monitor shell</b></article><article><span>Finish time</span><b>Hand-laced over hours per pair</b></article></div><div class=\"z05-engineering-body\"><div class=\"z05-build-card z05-engineering-specs\"><strong>AAW Z05 AuAg</strong><dl><dt>Format</dt><dd>Universal-fit hybrid in-ear monitor</dd><dt>Low End</dt><dd>10mm PET diaphragm dynamic woofer</dd><dt>Clarity</dt><dd>Dedicated mid and super-high balanced armature drivers</dd><dt>Voice Control</dt><dd>TwinCore Crossover Switch System</dd><dt>Pressure Flow</dt><dd>Bass-Flow Vent Pressure System</dd><dt>Finish</dt><dd>Forged-carbon faceplates; 3D-printed shells with hand-laced gold and silver foil finish</dd><dt>In The Box</dt><dd>2-pin detachable cable, 3.5mm, 4.4mm balanced, Type-C terminations, carrying case, LiquidMorph eartips</dd></dl></div><div class=\"z05-engineering-gallery\"><figure><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-gold-silver-faceplate-pair.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg gold and silver forged-carbon faceplates\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Au / Ag faceplates</b><span>Gold and silver foil are laced through the faceplate identity, not treated as a random surface effect.</span></figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-angled-shell-profile.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg angled 3D printed shell profile\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Universal shell geometry</b><span>The body remains a compact universal monitor shell, shaped around seal, nozzle angle, and long-session comfort.</span></figcaption></figure></div></div></div></section></div><style>.z05-engineering-section{background:#070707}.z05-engineering-head{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(360px,.92fr) minmax(420px,1.08fr);gap:54px;align-items:end}.z05-engineering-head h2{max-width:760px}.z05-engineering-copy{display:grid;gap:14px}.z05-engineering-copy p{margin:0;color:#d8d1c7;font-size:17px;line-height:1.62}.z05-craft-strip{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;margin:34px 0 0;background:rgba(255,255,255,.14);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14)}.z05-craft-strip article{background:#111;padding:20px 22px;min-height:104px}.z05-craft-strip span{display:block;margin-bottom:10px;color:#e2b768;font-size:12px;font-weight:900;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em}.z05-craft-strip b{display:block;color:#fff;font-size:19px;line-height:1.22}.z05-engineering-body{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(340px,.82fr) minmax(0,1.18fr);gap:24px;align-items:stretch;margin-top:24px}.z05-engineering-specs{padding:28px}.z05-engineering-specs dl{grid-template-columns:128px 1fr}.z05-engineering-gallery{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px}.z05-engineering-gallery figure{margin:0;position:relative;overflow:hidden;min-height:460px;background:#111;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12)}.z05-engineering-gallery img{display:block;width:100%;height:100%;min-height:460px;object-fit:cover}.z05-engineering-gallery figcaption{position:absolute;left:14px;right:14px;bottom:14px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.72);bor