                "custom_liquid": "<div id=\"z05-twincore\" class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z05-section dark z05-twincore-section\"><div class=\"z05-wrap z05-grid-2\"><div><p class=\"z05-kicker\">TwinCore Crossover Switch System</p><h2>Not a bass switch. Two ways to hear Z05.</h2><p>Most IEM switches feel like a small EQ nudge. TwinCore is different: it moves Z05 AuAg between two complete listening profiles, so bass weight, vocal position, treble air, and overall stage energy shift together.</p><p>Use it like you would choose gain, filter, or cartridge flavor in a serious hi-fi chain: one position for warmth and immersion, the other for focus and bite.</p><div class=\"z05-actions\"><a class=\"z05-btn\" href=\"/cart/add?id={{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}&quantity=1\">Buy Z05 AuAg</a></div></div><div class=\"z05-twincore-panel\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-twincore-switch-closeup.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg TwinCore switch with blue and red position markers\" loading=\"lazy\"><div class=\"z05-mode-grid\"><article><span>Blue Mode</span><h3>Weight / Flow</h3><p>Fuller low-end body, smoother upper harmonics, and a more relaxed center image for long sessions, vocals, jazz, pop, and immersive listening.</p></article><article><span>Red Mode</span><h3>Focus / Spark</h3><p>Tighter bass contour, more forward clarity, extra cymbal air, and a livelier edge for detail hunting, faster genres, and cleaner separation.</p></article></div></div></div></section></div><style>.z05-twincore-section{background:#050505}.z05-twincore-section h2{max-width:760px}.z05-twincore-section p{color:#d8d1c7}.z05-twincore-panel{background:#111;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);padding:12px}.z05-twincore-panel img{display:block;width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/10;object-fit:cover}.z05-mode-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;margin-top:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.14)}.z05-mode-grid article{background:#0b0b0b;padding:20px}.z05-mode-grid span{