                "section_visibility": "always",
                "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z05-section\"><div class=\"z05-wrap z05-grid-2\"><div><p class=\"z05-kicker\">FAQ</p><h2>Z05 AuAg buying notes</h2><p>Short answers for the questions listeners ask before choosing the AuAg Launch Edition.</p></div><div class=\"z05-faq\"><details open><summary>What does AuAg mean?</summary><p>AuAg names the Launch Edition decoration: Au for gold and Ag for silver. The right side carries gold accents and the left side carries silver accents. The forged-carbon treatment is on the faceplates; the 3D-printed shells are finished by hand with matching foil lacing.</p></details><details><summary>Is this only a cosmetic edition?</summary><p>No. The AuAg finish is the launch identity, but the listening story is the Z05 platform itself: dynamic bass, hybrid-driver clarity, Bass-Flow venting, and TwinCore switching.</p></details><details><summary>What does the TwinCore switch change?</summary><p>It changes the overall voicing. Blue mode leans fuller, smoother, and more grounded. Red mode leans cleaner, more open, and more energetic. The effect is broader than a simple bass boost.</p></details><details><summary>What cable is included?</summary><p>Z05 AuAg includes a 2-pin detachable cable with swappable 3.5mm stereo, 4.4mm balanced, and Type-C terminations, plus LiquidMorph eartips for its universal-fit seal.</p></details></div></div></section><section class=\"z05-final\"><div class=\"z05-wrap z05-final-inner\"><h2>Z05 AuAg: choose the mood, keep the monitor</h2><p>Those who listen will find the way.<br>善听者，终能找到道路。</p><p>A forged-carbon launch edition with dynamic-driver body, balanced-armature detail, and TwinCore control for the way you actually listen.</p><div class=\"z05-actions\"><a class=\"z05-btn\" href=\"/cart/add?id={{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}&quantity=1\">Buy Now</a></div></div></section><style>.z05-final{background:#0a0a0a;color:#fff;text-align:center;padding:7